<view class="page-container">
  <view class="page-header">
    <view class="page-header-left">
      <button class="back-btn" bindtap="goBack">◀</button>
      <text class="page-title">绑定家属</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="bind-tip">
    绑定家属后，您的生活动态将实时同步给他们，关爱如影随形。
  </view>

  <view class="form-area">
    <view class="input-group">
      <text class="input-label">家属姓名</text>
      <input class="input-field" type="text" placeholder="例如：儿子、女儿、老伴" value="{{name}}" bindinput="onNameInput" />
    </view>
    <view class="input-group">
      <text class="input-label">手机号码</text>
      <input class="input-field" type="text" placeholder="请输入11位手机号" value="{{phone}}" bindinput="onPhoneInput" />
    </view>
  </view>

  <button class="primary-btn" style="background:var(--color-secondary)" bindtap="handleBind">
    <text>立即绑定</text>
  </button>
</view>
